<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6; 
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container { 
      max-width: 600px; 
      margin: 40px auto; 
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header { 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #a78bfa 100%);
      color: white; 
      padding: 30px; 
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .content { 
      padding: 40px 30px;
      background: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #4b5563;
    }
    .otp-code { 
      font-size: 42px;
      letter-spacing: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #7c3aed;
      margin: 30px 0;
      padding: 25px;
      background: #f3f4f6;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 2px dashed #7c3aed;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .warning { 
      background: #fef3c7;
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .warning p {
      margin: 8px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #92400e;
    }
    .warning p:first-child {
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .footer { 
      text-align: center; 
      padding: 20px 30px; 
      background: #f9fafb;
      color: #6b7280; 
      font-size: 13px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>{{subject}}</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Use the verification code below to {{message}}:</p>
      
      <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
      
      <div class="warning">
        <p>⚠️ This code expires in 10 minutes</p>
        <p>For your security, never share this code with anyone — not even FormaChat support.</p>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">If you didn't request this code, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} FormaChat. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>